# Functional Design Document

## User Roles
1. **Employee**
   - Login
   - View own profile (name, department, pay rate)

2. **Employer**
   - Login
   - View all employees
   - Add a new employee
   - Update employee details
   - Delete an employee

## User Flows
### Employee
1. Login
2. Redirected to dashboard
3. See profile + pay rate

### Employer
1. Login
2. Redirected to admin dashboard
3. See list of all employees
4. Add / Edit / Delete employees
